Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.00,0:30:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我除了铁路以外还拥有了家庭\NIt's been a long time since I had a family
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.77,0:30:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}上次有这种感觉还是很久之前的事了\Nother than the railroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.91,0:30:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所以我想着今天早上我们可以一起去教堂\NSo I figured we could go to church this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.55,0:30:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果你愿意的话\Ntogether, if you're willing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.21,0:30:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我非常乐意\NI'd like that.
