Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.90,0:31:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}早上好\NMorning.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.34,0:31:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}问你个事\NSo let me ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.60,0:31:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}今天召集一队工人要多少钱\NHow much to get a crew together today?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.67,0:31:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你有多少钱\NHow much you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.68,0:31:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不够\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.07,0:31:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这点钱都召不到十个人\NCan't get more than ten men for that,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.07,0:31:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}而且最多干两小时\Ntwo hours, most.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.80,0:31:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}行吧  做完礼拜在山下等我\NAll right, meet you at the grade after church.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.81,0:31:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}大家伙儿们都盼着下午的棒球赛呢\NOh, boys been hankering for a game of baseball this afternoon.
