Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.68,0:31:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}伙计们\NFellas...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.88,0:31:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道今天是安息日  但是我们来活了\NI know it's the lord's day, but we're gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.73,0:32:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}杜兰特昨天来见我\NDurant came by to see me yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.07,0:32:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他想让我把你放了\NHe asked for your release.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.44,0:32:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我拒绝了他\NI told him no.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.91,0:32:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我有个提议  可以今天就还你自由\NI have a proposition that could free you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.68,0:32:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你签了这份文件  把赌场转交给我就行了\NSign this paper giving me title to the casino.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.99,0:32:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我还是会雇你打理那里\NI'll pay you to manage the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.08,0:32:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}当然了  我也可以直接把你的财产偷走\NGranted, I could just steal the property from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.68,0:32:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你早就这么干了\NYou already have.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.52,0:32:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我还是喜欢按法律办事\NI prefer to do things legally.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.99,0:32:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}200美元买下所有权\N$200 for the title...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.21,0:33:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}包括付你的工钱\Nsalary for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.37,0:33:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}杰瑟普会每周来收税\NJessup will pick up the tax every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.60,0:33:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}把你的臭钱收起来\NShove your money up your arse.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.86,0:33:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}别这样  麦克吉尼斯先生\NCome now, Mr. Mcginnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.06,0:33:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你是个聪明人\NYou're a smart man.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.37,0:33:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没错  也是个注定会成功的人\NAye. And a comer too.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.51,0:34:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我两手空空地来到这个国家\NI came to this country with nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.87,0:34:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}为自己打出了一片天下\Nand I built me a fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.87,0:34:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我会东山再起的\NI'll do it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.88,0:34:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我压根没义务讨你欢心\NBeholden not to the likes of you
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.84,0:34:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}或者讨托马斯·杜兰特欢心\Nor to Thomas C. Durant.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.18,0:34:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们绝对没法把这座山炸通\NWe damn sure can't blast through this mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.55,0:34:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}杜兰特也放弃了绕路的法子\NDurant's given up on going around.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.26,0:34:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}已经无计可施了\NGot no choice but over.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.34,0:34:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那顿暴打是不是还把你脑子打糊涂了\NThat beating you took done scrambled your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.70,0:34:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}测量员看遍了整座山\NSurveyors done been all over this mountain,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.15,0:34:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没找到一处平缓的地方\Nain't found nowhere that wasn't too steep.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.60,0:34:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是  我看了记录\NYeah, I looked at the notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.56,0:34:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}当时地上的积雪有六英尺\NThere was 6 foot of snow on the ground when they was out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.27,0:34:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我昨天在山顶  发现一个或许可行的办法\NNow, I was up top yesterday, saw a way might work.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.44,0:34:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}"或许"吗\N"Might"?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.08,0:34:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果我们能沿着山的边缘\NIf we carve a ledge the width of a train track
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.18,0:34:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}凿出铺设铁轨的路\Non the mountain's outer edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.99,0:34:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你看\NAll right, look...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.07,0:34:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-看到那边的悬崖了吗  -看到了\N- See that cliff over yonder? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.89,0:34:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们在那凿出两度的斜坡\NWe gonna dig a 2% grade straight for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.22,0:34:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}等我知道两小时我们能凿多远\NWhen I know how far we can get in two hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.19,0:34:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就能算出全体工人需要多久能到山顶\NI can figure how long it'll take a full crew to reach the summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.95,0:34:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}杜兰特没让我们这么做\NCould be Durant ain't have us try this
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.34,0:34:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}因为他知道不可能\N'cause he know it's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.98,0:35:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}只有一个办法能知道了\NWell, only one way to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.39,0:35:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}来了吗\NDid it come?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.39,0:35:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这是芬奇主教发来的\NThis is from Bishop Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.24,0:35:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这上面说达森主教身高五尺六寸\NIt says Bishop Dutson is 5 feet, 6 inches tall,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.03,0:35:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}棕色头发\Nbrown hair,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.13,0:35:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}身材健壮\Nportly girth.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.65,0:35:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}站起来\NStand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.20,0:36:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你不是这封电报里说的人\NYou are not the man described in this telegram.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.95,0:36:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.56,0:36:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你欺骗了我们整个族群\NYou have deceived this entire community.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.38,0:36:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}告诉我你是谁\NTell me who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.49,0:36:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我是\NI am...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.13,0:36:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}约瑟夫·达森主教\NBishop Joseph Dutson,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.82,0:36:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我从没见过芬奇主教\Nand I have never met Bishop Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.56,0:36:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们共事过三年\NYou prayed beside him for three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.51,0:36:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这个证明\NThis proves
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.41,0:36:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你欺骗了我们所有人\Nthat you have borne false witness to us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.70,0:36:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这只能证明发报人撒谎\NIt proves only that the author has lied
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.86,0:36:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}以印证你的幻觉\Nto support your delusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.72,0:36:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}或者你就是发报人\NOr perhaps you are the author,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.79,0:36:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}海彻兄弟\NBrother Hatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.57,0:37:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我要把这个送去长老会\NI am bringing this to the Elders.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.52,0:37:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们会判你有罪\NThey will find you guilty
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.48,0:37:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}送你上绞架的\Nand set you to the noose.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.48,0:37:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你确定他们有权吊死主教吗\NAre you sure they have the authority to hang a bishop?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.51,0:37:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}因为如果他们无权  你又错了\NBecause if they do not and you are wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.74,0:37:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那被吊死的会是你  海彻兄弟\Nthen you will hang, Brother Hatch,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.93,0:37:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还有长老们\Nas will the Elders.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.65,0:37:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果长老会无权  那谁有\NWho has the authority, if not the Elders?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.54,0:37:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一位无可指责的人\NAn unimpeachable man...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.56,0:37:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}上帝的雄狮\Nthe lion of the lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.42,0:37:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们的兄弟  杨百翰\Nour brother Brigham Young.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.86,0:37:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}请他来\NBring him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.19,0:38:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我会听从他的审判\NI will abide by his judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.33,0:39:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们用的工具不对\NThese tools all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.94,0:39:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没用的\NThis ain't gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.69,0:39:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}感谢各位祝我献身\NThank you for helping me consecrate
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.55,0:39:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这座美丽的圣殿\Nthis fine house of worship.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.24,0:39:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}兄弟姐妹们\NBrothers and sisters,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.27,0:39:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}耶稣在世\NJesus Christ is alive
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.86,0:39:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}并显身于此\Nand present in this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.11,0:39:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果我们不接受他做自己的上帝与救世主\NAnd if we do not accept him as our personal lord and savior,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.02,0:39:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们会焚身地狱\Nwe will burn in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.98,0:39:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}阿门\NAmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.81,0:39:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我说的只是有罪之人\NI speak not of the innocents among us.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.37,0:39:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}上帝说过\NThe Lord said,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.59,0:39:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}"让小孩到我这里来\N"Suffer the children to come unto me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.65,0:39:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}天堂是属于他们之地"\NThe kingdom of heaven belongs to such as these."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.83,0:40:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是那些背叛上帝\NNo, it is those who turn away
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.08,0:40:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}破坏教义的人\Nfrom the teachings of the lord
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.99,0:40:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}堕入地狱不得翻身\Nwho will spend eternity in the fiery lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.39,0:40:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}上帝要求我们敬爱神明\NFor he commands us to love our god,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.16,0:40:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}也敬爱自己的邻居\Nas well as our neighbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.10,0:40:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们敬爱神明吗\NDo you love your god?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.89,0:40:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.11,0:40:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}敬爱邻居吗\NDo you love your neighbor?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.62,0:40:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.25,0:40:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我这周没有敬爱自己的邻居\NI did not love my neighbor this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.15,0:40:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}与同伴妄下论断\NI sat in judgment on my fellow man.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.90,0:40:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我被自己的\NI reveled in the pit
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.74,0:40:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}伪善所蒙蔽\Nof my own self-righteousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.57,0:40:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我理应被逐入黑暗\NSo I deserve to be cast out into darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.11,0:40:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不值得救赎\Nand I do not deserve salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.35,0:40:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们都是\NNone of us does.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.39,0:40:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}只有耶稣的怜恤能拯救我们\NOnly the blessed mercy of Jesus Christ can save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.73,0:41:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你好啊  小家伙\NHey, little man.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.34,0:41:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我去了教堂\NI went to church.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.99,0:41:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-娜奥米...  -我知道\N- Naomi... - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.47,0:42:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不会再问了\NI'll stop asking.

